## Relay to #control-center

Post after resync if risk was YELLOW or RED:

```
slack_send_message(
  channel_id: "C0AGTB4Q30S",
  message: "[<SlotName>] /resync: <N> commits behind main → rebased. Risk: <GREEN/YELLOW/RED>\n*Overlap:* <files touched by both>"
)
```

Skip on GREEN (routine). Always post on YELLOW/RED.
